<div id="Snake_plant" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Snake_plant.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Snake_plant">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Snake plant</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Snake_plant')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Snake_plant');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">The snake plant, commonly referred to as mother-in-law's tongue, is a resilient succulent that can grow anywhere between 6 inches to several feet.</p>
