<div id="Aloe_vera" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Aloe_vera_plant.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Aloe_vera">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Aloe vera</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Aloe_vera')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Aloe_vera');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">The botanical name of Aloe vera is Aloe barbadensis miller. It belongs to Asphodelaceae (Liliaceae) family, and is a shrubby or arborescent, perennial, xerophytic, succulent, pea- green color plant.</p>
